    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Machines for composing type that do not employ hot-metal casting at the time of composition.  Includes those that assemble foundry type mechanically and those that do strike-on composition.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
